Package: codeagent
Title: An AI Coding Agent for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kaiping", "Yang", email = "kaiping.yang@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R-native agentic coding assistant powered by the Claude API via
    'ellmer'. Provides a full-featured coding agent with streaming output,
    tool execution, permission management, context compaction, skill system,
    and an interactive 'Shiny' UI. Designed as an R equivalent of the
    Claude Code CLI.
